      "title": "‎",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## MisoTTS-ComfyUI Model Requirements\n\n**VRAM:** BF16 MisoTTS needs about **18-20 GB VRAM** during generation. FP32 is much heavier.  \nMisoTTS has **Aimdo / ComfyUI model-management integration** for unload and VRAM visualization.\n\n**misotts** (main model, tokenizer, Mimi codec)\n\n- [🤗 model.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/MisoLabs/MisoTTS/resolve/main/model.safetensors) — official fp32\n- [🤗 misotts-bf16.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/MisoTTS-BF16) — BF16, recommended\n- [🤗 unsloth/Llama-3.2-1B](https://huggingface.co/unsloth/Llama-3.2-1B) — tokenizer mirror\n- [🤗 kyutai/moshiko-pytorch-bf16](https://huggingface.co/kyutai/moshiko-pytorch-bf16) — Mimi codec\n\n**audio_encoders** (optional Whisper transcript node)\n\n- [🤗 openai/whisper-large-v3-turbo](https://huggingface.co/openai/whisper-large-v3-turbo)\n\n## Model Storage Location\n\n```text\nComfyUI/\n└── models/\n    ├── misotts/\n    │   ├── model.safetensors\n    │   ├── misotts-bf16.safetensors\n    │   ├── tokenizers/\n    │   │   └── unsloth_Llama-3.2-1B/\n    │   └── codecs/\n    │       └── kyutai_moshiko-pytorch-bf16/\n    │           └── tokenizer-e351c8d8-checkpoint125.safetensors\n    └── audio_encoders/\n        └── openai_whisper-large-v3-turbo/\n```\n\nIf `download_if_missing` is enabled, the nodes download missing assets to these folders automatically.\n\n**Links**\n\n- [Issues](https://github.com/Saganaki22/MisoTTS-ComfyUI/issues)\n- [Saganaki22/MisoTTS-ComfyUI](https://github.com/Saganaki22/MisoTTS-ComfyUI)\n- [Original MisoTTS Repo](https://github.com/MisoLabsAI/MisoTTS)"
      ],
      "color": "#222",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
